item.title: Introduction to Scan Types
item.description: A Little Background I’ve always been interested in knowing how to hack. It’s what got me interested in programming, and it started out with wanting to gain advantages in games. Though now I’ve become interested in further improving my knowledge and skills in computer science. With this series of hacking articles, I plan to write about my journey. I want to challenge myself in different areas (writing, programming, thinking, explaining), make this a hobby, and improve my writing skills.
